==製作==
最初於2011年由[[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]聘請的[[麥克斯·蘭迪斯|麥克斯·蘭迪斯]]撰寫劇本<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/frankenstein-coming-life-fox-204693 |title=Frankenstein Coming To Life for Fox |publisher=Hollywoodreporter.com |date=22 June 2011 |accessdate=26 November 2013 |archive-date=2020-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200510040943/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/frankenstein-coming-life-fox-204693 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年9月，宣布[[保羅·麥格根|保羅·麥格根]]擔任導演<ref>{{cite web |first=Borys |last=Kit |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/frankenstein-paul-mcguinan-368160 |title='Sherlock' Director Boards Fox's 'Frankenstein' |publisher=Hollywoodreporter.com |date=5 September 2012 |accessdate=26 November 2013 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111193546/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/frankenstein-paul-mcguinan-368160 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年3月，[[丹尼爾·雷德克里夫|丹尼爾·雷德克里夫]]加入電影飾演{{link-en|伊果|Igor (character)}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/daniel-radcliffe-is-foxs-frankenstein-20130228|title=Daniel Radcliffe Is Putting It Together For Fox's 'Frankenstein'|first=Kevin|last=Jagernauth|date=28 February 2013|publisher=indiewire.com|accessdate=1 March 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130302070149/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/daniel-radcliffe-is-foxs-frankenstein-20130228|archive-date=2013-03-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；2013年7月，[[詹姆斯·麥艾維|詹姆斯·麥艾維]]將飾演主角{{link-en|維克多·弗蘭肯斯坦|Victor Frankenstein}}<ref name="deadline1"/>。2013年9月，[[潔西卡·布朗·芬德莉|潔西卡·布朗·芬德莉]]加入劇組<ref name="deadline2"/>。

電影的攝製大多於[[英國|英國]]進行，拍攝地點包括{{link-en|朗克羅斯製片廠|Longcross Studios|朗克羅斯}}、{{link-en|特威克納姆電影製片廠|Twickenham Film Studios}}和{{link-en|查塔姆歷史造船廠|Chatham Historic Dockyard}}<ref>{{cite web |author=Pippa Considine |url=http://www.televisual.com/news-detail/McGuigans-Frankenstein-starts-Twickenham-based-shoot_nid-3591.html |title=News & Comments |publisher=Televisual |date=2013-11-29 |accessdate=2014-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203053042/http://www.televisual.com/news-detail/McGuigans-Frankenstein-starts-Twickenham-based-shoot_nid-3591.html |archive-date=2013-12-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。主要拍攝於2013年11月25日，直至2014年3月20日結束<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theknowledgeonline.com/the-knowledge-bulletin/post/2013/11/25/James-McAvoy-brings-Frankensteins-monster-to-life |title=James McAvoy brings Frankenstein to life | The Knowledge Bulletin | The Knowledge |publisher=Theknowledgeonline.com |date=2013-11-25 |accessdate=2014-05-18 |archive-date=2020-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810123411/https://www.theknowledgeonline.com/the-knowledge-bulletin/post/2013/11/25/James-McAvoy-brings-Frankensteins-monster-to-life |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.studiosystemnews.com/on-the-set-for-32414/ |title=‘On The Set’ For 3/24/14: Nicole Kidman Starts ‘Strangerland’, ‘Frankenstein’ Wraps For 20th Century Fox |publisher=Studiosystemnews.com |date= |accessdate=2014-05-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140528092725/http://www.studiosystemnews.com/on-the-set-for-32414/ |archivedate=2014-05-28 }}</ref>。

