[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]專業評級24%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/victor_frankenstein_2015/ |title=Victor Frankenstein reviews |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=November 25, 2015 |archive-date=2020-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210123307/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/victor_frankenstein_2015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分34<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/victor-frankenstein |title=Victor Frankenstein reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=November 25, 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112021702/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/victor-frankenstein |dead-url=no }}</ref>，主要獲得負面評價；影評人認為電影雖然給了科學怪人故事一個新的視角，但仍不足提升觀眾的興趣。

